<h2 class="text-headline-lg font-headline-lg text-white">About <span class="text-primary">Me</span></h2>
<p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">My journey as a developer is driven by a deep curiosity for how things work under the hood. I am a passionate developer who loves bridging the gap between design and code, ensuring that every pixel serves a purpose while maintaining a robust technical foundation.</p>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant/80">Whether it's designing efficient database schemas with PostgreSQL or crafting reactive frontends with Next.js, I approach every project with a relentless focus on problem-solving and operational efficiency.</p>
