<h2 class="text-headline-lg font-headline-lg text-white">Services I Provide</h2>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">I offer design and development services focused on building fast, modern, and user-friendly digital experiences.</p>
</div>
<!-- Updated Grid for Services: 4 columns, 2 rows -->
