<h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 text-lg">Full-Stack Web Development</h3>
<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">End-to-end web applications using React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB with clean architecture and scalable code.</p>
