<h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 text-lg">Backend &amp; API Development</h3>
<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Secure and efficient REST APIs using Node.js and Express, optimized for performance and scalability.</p>
</div>
<!-- Service 4 -->
