<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-primary">storage</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 text-lg">Database Design &amp; Management</h3>
<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Well-structured MongoDB databases with optimized queries for speed, reliability, and data integrity.</p>
</div>
<!-- Service 5 -->
<div class="gradient-border-card p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-primary">lock</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 text-lg">Authentication &amp; Authorization</h3>
<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Implementation of secure login systems using JWT, role-based access control, and best security practices.</p>
</div>
<!-- Service 6 -->
